"Extensions often need to invoke the ``python`` interpreter from the Python "
"installation being extended. This routine can put a ``python`` Executable as "
"a global in the module scope for the extension package to simplify extension "
"installs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../_spack_root/lib/spack/spack/package_base.py:docstring of
#: spack.package_base.PackageBase.setup_dependent_package:11
