"architecture. Mutation cannot change the spec name, namespace, dependencies, "
"or abstract_hash. Any attribute which is unset will not be touched. Variant "
"values can be replaced with the literal ``None`` to remove the variant. "
"``None`` as a variant value is represented by ``VariantValue(..., (None,))``."
