"using the ``\"spawn\"`` start method. Notably, installations are performed "
"in a subprocess and require transmitting the Package object (in such a way "
"that the repository is available for importing when it is deserialized); "
"installations performed in Spack unit tests may include additional "
"modifications to global state in memory that must be replicated in the child "
"process."
