#: spack.variant.prevalidate_variant_value:3
msgid ""
"This checks that the variant value is valid for *some* definition of the "
"variant, and it raises if we know *before* concretization that the value "
"cannot occur. On success it returns the variant definitions for which the "
"variant is valid."
msgstr ""

